data.description: Experience the beauty of breathtaking mountain views from this wonderful corner lot home in Apache Junction! This gem welcomes you with a private courtyard and a charming front patio, the perfect spot to savor your morning coffee while taking in the scenery. Once inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the spacious & airy living & dining room boasting Saltillo tile flooring, abundant natural light, exposed beams on the vaulted ceilings, and a cozy fireplace, promising warm and inviting evenings. The kitchen comes stainless steel appliances. Additionally, a formal family room provides a dedicated space for relaxation and entertainment. The large primary retreat is a haven of tranquility, complete with direct outdoor access and a private bathroom. Home is in need of repairs. Lastly, the generous backyard has a storage shed and a covered patio, excellent for outdoor dining or simply enjoying the fresh air. Don't wait any longer. Embrace the Arizona lifestyle you've been dreaming of!
